replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更為無恥的是，有一次宋太宗趙光義臨幸小周后還把宮廷畫師召來，小周后在不知情的情況下慘遭侮辱。當小周后看到趙光義身後竟然有幾位長須老人提着畫筆觀摩他們之時，小周后一腳蹬開了趙光義，說什麼也不從。而趙光義並不善罷甘休，召來十幾個宮女強行按住小周后...之後便有了《熙陵幸小周后圖》<br />\n<br />\n嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天道有輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5987869791d2f7e544c9bfa24c8c2f4c37506044","tid":455022,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金人算唔算支那人</blockquote><br />\n東北雞黎既</blockquote><br />\n被中華民族左喇"},{"pid":"596bb0bffce5dfa5f1eb0af290051b9b283e8e58","tid":455022,"uid":30673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宋太祖殺入後官當眾老強小周后又如何！</blockquote><br />\ndetail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪蘿莉</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2bc05ed57ded7edfac209066684ffddef30387","tid":455022,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>宋太祖殺入後官當眾老強小周后又如何！</blockquote><br />\n好似係太宗唔係太祖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇過文兩兄弟都有<br />\n<br />\n宋太宗正Ｄ<br />\n<br />\n小周后為了李後主屈辱求生尚可勉強地半推半就，當此次行將就事時，她竟然發現數名山羊鬍子的老頭，從宮緯後戰戰兢兢地探頭出來現場寫生，於是僅存的一丁點可憐的自尊爆發出來，一腳蹬開宋太宗，驚恐萬狀地躲入龍床後，任宋太宗怎麼威逼利誘她死活都不肯再就範。宋太宗強推、力按仍無法得手，惱怒之餘竟又喝來數名宮女代為強抓小周后，終又強幸之，並使畫師完整錄下。這就是中國歷史上最著名的春宮圖之一《熙陵幸小周后圖》，「熙陵」指宋太宗，因為他死後葬在河南鞏縣的永熙陵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1nnuaj6/3155/6108761172.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1nnuaj6%2F3155%2F6108761172.jpg&d=5vWcKq%2FNKKtnvWSXd8ZgDozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=76f11361\" target=\"_blank\">https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1nnuaj6/3155/6108761172.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n圖"},{"pid":"956b34337e423cc3d0424808e684463f893b9997","tid":455022,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:47:29.000Z","msg":"見到topic名都笑:"},{"pid":"52848f228adce4d1eff3fd2e27fd3b9233c3eab9","tid":455022,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T09:19:41.000Z","msg":"一將功成萬骨枯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起投名狀, 搶錢搶糧搶女人"},{"pid":"af345a418012e06185fcb0c8e0c6ea62c78211cc","tid":455022,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"講真如果八國聯軍或者之後日本食左東亞<br />\n會唔會58族共融或者51族共融"},{"pid":"e925211ba8ff1adef15ea505344114e7641fd8a5","tid":455022,"uid":107086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>靖康恥 猶未雪<br />\n<br />\n臣子恨 何時滅<br />\n<br />\n駕長車踏破賀蘭山缺<br />\n<br />\n壯志饑餐胡虜肉，笑談渴飲匈奴血<br />\n<br />\n岳飛真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪又係軍閥一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偏安政權已經有個皇帝都仲日日夜夜要接原來兩個返歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔接其實唔使死 so9sad</blockquote><br />\n有呢個如果就唔會係岳飛啦"},{"pid":"630417edaad4cbc77f1363f88fece78f86ec536d","tid":455022,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"其實啲金人而家喺邊? 上面只係得蒙古?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9448734e3e01c6b4cf6ea288f097f2e78cb33f","tid":455022,"uid":37989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實啲金人而家喺邊? 上面只係得蒙古?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n滿族人囉咪即係"},{"pid":"ce755262de40c960aa279a4b1f8a8f1c3f759f3c","tid":455022,"uid":58998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"